<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md border border-orange-100 p-6 space-y-6">
    <div class="text-center space-y-2">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-700">管理者ページ</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
        予約管理・カレンダー設定・管理者追加を行えます。
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-3">
      <%= link_to admin_reservations_path,
                  class: "w-full inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-green-600 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-white shadow hover:bg-green-700 transition" do %>
        <span>予約一覧へ</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <% end %>

      <%= link_to admin_calendar_events_path,
                  class: "w-full inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-orange-500 px-4 py-3 font-bold text-white shadow hover:bg-orange-600 transition" do %>
        <span>カレンダー設定へ</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <% end %>

      <%= link_to admin_admins_path,
                  class: "w-full inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-3 font-bold text-green-700 border border-green-200 shadow-sm hover:bg-green-50 transition" do %>
        <span>管理者一覧（追加・削除）</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <% end %>

      <%= link_to admin_harvest_experiences_path,
                  class: "w-full inline-flex items-center justify-between rounded-md bg-white px-4 py-3 font-bold text-orange-600 border border-orange-200 shadow-sm hover:bg-orange-50 transition" do %>
        <span>収穫体験管理</span>
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="pt-2 border-t border-gray-100 text-center space-y-2">
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">
        ※ 管理者一覧の操作は慎重に行ってください（最後の管理者は削除不可）。
      </p>

      <%= button_to "ログアウト",
                    admin_logout_path,
                    method: :delete,
                    form: { data: { turbo_confirm: "ログアウトしますか？" } },
                    class: "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-gray-100 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-200 transition" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
